        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_902d71e6">
            <lb />An Important Message
            <lb />For Dealers Who Desire A Reproducing Piano for a Leader
            <lb />The <name type="brand">WELTE-MIGNON</name>
            <lb />Is the <name type="brand">Original
            <lb />REPRODUCING PIANO</name>
            <lb />And Was the First Ever Sold in the World

            <cb />
            <lb /><name type="brand">The Original Welte-Mignon Reproduc-
            <lb />ing Piano</name> as manufactured by the new
            <lb /><orgName>Welte-Mignon Corp.</orgName> is the finest product
            <lb />of its kind in the world.
            <lb />The new <orgName>Welte-Mignon Corp.</orgName> is not only
            <lb />strongly entreched financially, but has a
            <lb />very able staff of executives of proven ability,
            <lb />who are pursuing a policy of producing only
            <lb />the highest quality instruments - Grand
            <lb />Pianos under the name of <name type="brand">"Welte"</name>,
            <name type="brand">"Welte-
            <lb />Mignon"</name> Reproducing Pianos and Organs,
            <lb />grands of various sizes in conventional and
            <lb />period designs. The <name type="brand">WELTE-MIGNON</name>
            <lb />franchise is a valuable one for the leader.

            <cb/>
            <lb /><name type="brand">The Original Welte-Mignon</name> as manufac-
            <lb />tured by the new <orgName>Welte-Mignon Corp.</orgName>
            <lb />not only retains all the marvelous features
            <lb />invented by <persName>Edwin Welte</persName>, but also has many
            <lb />refinements in manufacture which places it
            <lb />in its rightful position as THE reproducing
            <lb />piano. We invite comparison.
            <lb /><name type="brand">The Original Welte-Mignon</name> is found in grands
            <lb />which in every way meet the requirements
            <lb />of the most representative music merchants.

            <lb />The <name type="brand">Welte-Mignon Library</name>
            <lb />1st Most Comprehensive. It Comprises Several Thousand Recordings That Reproduce
            <lb />
            <seg
                ana="#analogy_to_photography" resp="#np" type="topic">
                With Photographic Accuracy
            </seg> the Individual Playing of
            the Master Pianists of the World<lb />
